movie.title: Hollywoodland
movie.plot: The complicated life and controversial suicide of George Reeves is investigated by a fictional private detective who finds that there are reasons to suspect that Reeves may not have killed himself after all. The detective also finds that there is a little of George Reeves in himself, and maybe, each of us.
movie.awards: Nominated for 1 Golden Globe. Another 3 wins & 7 nominations.
